OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781024765
OL,3,CPreston Davey was left at the 'mercy'
OL,4,Cof adoptive parent, murder trial hears
OL,6,FA baby was left at the "mercy" of an
OL,7,Fabusive adoptive parent and paid with
OL,8,Fhis life, a court heard.
OL,10,FPreston Davey, aged 13 months, died
OL,11,Fafter months of alleged sexual and
OL,12,Fphysical abuse by high school head of
OL,13,Fyear Jamie Varley, 37, Preston Crown
OL,14,FCourt heard.
OL,16,FVarley, accused of murder and 25 other
OL,17,Foffences, was adopting the boy with
OL,18,Fhis partner, John McGowan-Fazakerley,
OL,19,F32, who is accused of causing or
OL,20,Fallowing the death of a child, child
OL,21,Fcruelty and sexual assault.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
