PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781024765
OL,3,CPreston Davey was left at the 'mercy'
OL,4,Cof adoptive parent, murder trial hears
OL,6,FBoth men deny a sexual interest in the
OL,7,Fchild and have pleaded not guilty to
OL,8,Fall charges.
OL,10,FPeter Wright KC, in his closing speech
OL,11,Fto the jury in the seventh week of the
OL,12,Ftrial, said: "Preston Davey was just
OL,13,Fnine months old when he was placed
OL,14,Fwith these defendants for adoption.
OL,16,F"It was supposed to be, you may
OL,17,Fconclude, the start of a new life
OL,18,Ftogether for each of them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781024765
OL,3,CPreston Davey was left at the 'mercy'
OL,4,Cof adoptive parent, murder trial hears
OL,6,F"Yet just a few days short of four
OL,7,Fmonths later Preston was dead and his
OL,8,Fbody contained injuries both external
OL,9,Fand internal we say, consistent with
OL,10,Fhis abuse."
OL,12,FMr Wright said it was only after
OL,13,FPreston began living at their home in
OL,14,FBlackpool, in April 2023, that he
OL,15,Fbegan to suffer non-accidental
OL,16,F"cluster" injuries of bruising,
OL,17,Fseizures or respiratory failures and
OL,18,Fevidence of abnormality of his anatomy.
OL,20,FHe suggested the "common denominator"
OL,21,Fwas when he was left alone with Varley.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781024765
OL,3,CPreston Davey was left at the 'mercy'
OL,4,Cof adoptive parent, murder trial hears
OL,6,FMr Wright said Varley's sexual
OL,7,Finterest in Preston was evident
OL,8,F"within weeks" of his placement, an
OL,9,Finterest "shared" by his partner,
OL,10,Fshown by the alleged indecent images
OL,11,Fand videos taken of the child.
OL,13,FThe prosecutor added: "Preston's death
OL,14,Fwas a tragedy waiting to happen. Mr
OL,15,FMcGowan-Fazakerley knew that but chose
OL,16,Fto ignore it."
OL,18,FThe cause of Preston's death was found
OL,19,Fto be acute upper airways obstruction
OL,20,Fby either smothering or an object or
OL,21,Fobjects inserted into his mouth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781024765
OL,3,CPreston Davey was left at the 'mercy'
OL,4,Cof adoptive parent, murder trial hears
OL,6,FA post-mortem examination found 40
OL,7,Fexternal and internal trauma injuries
OL,8,Fto the child's body, consistent with
OL,9,F"forcible penetration" and sexual
OL,10,Fabuse and ruled out drowning as a
OL,11,Fcause of death.
OL,13,FPreston had been rushed to Blackpool
OL,14,FVictoria Hospital on July 27 2023,
OL,15,Fwith Varley telling medical staff he
OL,16,Fhad left the child in the bath for two
OL,17,For three minutes and returned to find
OL,18,Fhim submerged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781024765
OL,3,CPreston Davey was left at the 'mercy'
OL,4,Cof adoptive parent, murder trial hears
OL,6,FMr Wright said: "As Preston lay dying,
OL,7,Fhe needed an explanation and the
OL,8,Fcharade then followed."
OL,10,FHe reminded jurors the child was noted
OL,11,Fas having dry hair, was wearing a
OL,12,Fnappy, the bath tub was empty of water
OL,13,Fand no water was found in his lungs.
OL,15,FAnd he recalled how witness Janet Gee,
OL,16,Fa work colleague of Varley, told the
OL,17,Fcourt how Varley had told her of his
OL,18,F"dark thoughts" about drowning or
OL,19,Fsuffocating the child.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781024765
OL,3,CPreston Davey was left at the 'mercy'
OL,4,Cof adoptive parent, murder trial hears
OL,6,FConcluding his closing speech, the
OL,7,Fprosecutor added: "Preston was at the
OL,8,Fmercy of Jamie Varley on the 27th of
OL,9,FJuly, and paid for it with his life."
OL,11,FVarley denies murder, manslaughter,
OL,12,Ftwo counts of assault by penetration,
OL,13,Ffive counts of cruelty to a child,
OL,14,Fgrievous bodily harm, sexual assault
OL,15,Fof a child, 13 counts of taking
OL,16,Findecent photos or videos of a child,
OL,17,Fone of distributing an indecent photo
OL,18,Fof a child, to his co-accused, and one
OL,19,Fof making an indecent photo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
