PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1781024765
OL,3,CPreston Davey was left at the 'mercy'
OL,4,Cof adoptive parent, murder trial hears
OL,6,FMcGowan-Fazakerley denies allowing the
OL,7,Fdeath of a child, three counts of
OL,8,Fchild cruelty and one count of the
OL,9,Fsexual assault of a child.
OL,11,FThe trial was adjourned until Tuesday
OL,12,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
